---
import LegalLayout from '../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
---

<LegalLayout
  title="Subscription Terms — Recursio"
  description="Subscription Terms for Recursio SMART and PRO plans."
  canonicalSlug="subscription-terms"
>
  <article class="legal-section">
    <h1>Subscription Terms</h1>

    <h2>1. Overview</h2>
    <p>
      Recursio offers optional auto-renewable subscriptions that unlock additional learning
      features. Available plans: <strong>PRACTICE</strong> (free), <strong>SMART</strong> (paid),
      <strong>PRO</strong> (paid).
    </p>

    <h2>2. Plans</h2>
    <p>
      <strong>SMART</strong> may include: AI Writing feedback, AI grammar explanations, AI Coach
      practice, more AI turns, larger vocabulary capacity.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>PRO</strong> may include: everything in SMART, premium dictation voices, higher AI
      limits, deeper progress insights, multiple vocabulary spaces.
    </p>
    <p>Features are subject to change as described in Section 9.</p>

    <h2>3. Billing</h2>
    <p>
      Subscriptions are billed through the App Store or Google Play. Prices are shown before
      purchase and may vary by region. Recursio does not directly process payment card
      information.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Renewal</h2>
    <p>
      Subscriptions automatically renew unless canceled through the relevant app store account
      settings before the renewal date.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Cancellation</h2>
    <p>
      Users can cancel through Apple App Store account subscription settings or Google Play
      subscription settings. Canceling prevents future renewals but does not necessarily refund
      the current billing period.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Restore Purchases</h2>
    <p>
      Users can restore purchases in the Recursio app if supported by the platform.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Refunds</h2>
    <p>
      Refunds are handled by Apple or Google according to their store policies.
    </p>

    <h2>8. Plan Changes</h2>
    <p>
      Users may be able to upgrade, downgrade, or change billing periods through the App Store or
      Google Play.
    </p>

    <h2>9. Feature Changes</h2>
    <p>
      Subscription features and limits may change over time. Any material changes will be
      reflected in the app and these terms.
    </p>

    <h2>10. Contact</h2>
    <p>
      <a href="mailto:support@recursio.app">support@recursio.app</a>
    </p>
  </article>
</LegalLayout>
